data.description: Located in the beautiful and convenient Laurel Mountain Ranch subdivision, this home is located minutes from major highways and shopping! Upon entry of the home, you are greeted with a large open floor plan that is perfect for large family gatherings yet cozy enough for a movie night at home! There is ZERO carpet in the home! The large kitchen overlooks the living space and is full of natural light throughout the entire home! The home has extra living space upstairs that can be a media room, office, playroom or whatever you desire! The master bedroom is large and privately tucked away and includes a large garden tub and separate shower. The community includes a pool and park! Make sure and go see this home today!
